{"tid":1516464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 被捕需知：李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」 (文字版+有片)","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:11:23.000Z","uid":127929,"like":104,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd22db73c0457497dd64bbfe3d7b35155db4443","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」 (文字版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512130</a><br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n文字版 (如果打漏請大家幫手補充)<br />\n小弟平時做student helper打開錄音稿, 總算叫做有d嘢可以做下<br />\n有少少長, 但係希望大家可以睇曬, TLDR 版本喺最底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>關於「我無嘢講」</em></span></strong></ins><br />\n「我無嘢講」唔係淨係對住黑警嘅時候無嘢講, <br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你被捕之後做所有嘢任何嘢都要無嘢講</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為一旦被捕, <span style=\"font-size: large;\">警察最想做到嘅事就係<strong><em>調查</em></strong>然後<strong><em>指證</em></strong>你</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你越同黑警合作 = 你配合佢告鳩你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n你係無任何責任需要配合黑警去調查 + 指責你自己同被捕人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以無論任何情況下都唔可以講任何嘢, 唔係淨係對住黑警冇嘢講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>例如有咩情況呢:</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n被捕人士當中有係臥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喺旅遊巴/警車運送途中入面有臥底</span></strong>, <br />\n喺香港法律底下一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">臥底聽到任何一句說話, 而嗰句說道係可以指證你係法咗犯</span></strong>的話, <br />\n嗰個臥底<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可以將嗰個說話呈堂</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n去到狗屋後有機會有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">家長</span></span></span></strong>探你,<br />\n咁班狗就可以同家長講「依家小朋友已經喺警察二十幾個鐘, 但係冇機會同佢進行一個調查, <strong><em>因為小朋友選擇唔講嘢, 所以個程序一路都唔可以開始</em></strong>」, <br />\n<br />\n咁無知嘅家長可能就會同小朋友講「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不如你同黑警配合, 快D講曬個故事, 就可以快D做保釋</span></span>快D走」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n <br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>無嘢講係包括同身邊所有人包括同家長</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為當你同家長講嘢, 身邊會有個黑警喺度, 因為個黑警會擔心你同家長通風報信, 喺佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上屋搜證之前家長將你所有嘢Dum曬</span></strong>,<br />\n所以家長見面時/ 打電話搵家長+律師時都會有黑警喺你旁邊一路聽你任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一旦被捕.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> 緊記係所有程序都係「我無嘢講」. 並唔係淨係指面對黑警時</strong></span></span><br />\n呢個會係對自己最大嘅保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你會認為快d講曬所有程序出嚟快d保釋快d脫離狗屋<br />\n其實被捕之後, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黑警一係揀釋放你, 一係揀告你上法庭</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係喺呢個過程中, 你講嘅任何說話幫助黑警指證你的話, 你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留底嘅案底, 會係一世</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你自己可以評價下, <strong><em>留喺狗屋48小時</em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係 <em><strong>留低d證據比黑警遲d指證你 留一世案底</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n係一個案件入面, 黑警唔需要有任何人證/物證, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>只要你喺份證供入面承認咗自己犯罪, 嗰份證據就算只係唯一嘅證據, 都足以令你定罪</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以, 「我無嘢講」四字係一定需要記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>點解要咁強調? </ins></strong></span><br />\n因為喺狗屋入面你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未必有機會一定見到律師</span></strong>, 律師可能好早去到狗屋, 但係班狗可以有好多原因令律師見你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如「所有會客室都被唔同律師團隊用緊, 冇房比其他律師用」<br />\n所以當無律師嚟到嘅時候你無嘢講, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔提供任何嘢比班狗入你, 係對自己最大保障</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>「我無嘢講」的風險</ins></strong></span><br />\n假設你係一清二白, 真係好冤枉, 你可能只係路過, 就比人話你「非法集結」比人拉咗, cctv都影埋, 咁喺狗屋入面你乜都唔講嘅風險就係<br />\n<br />\n<em>你會被告上法庭, 你同法官講你只係路過, 若然律師信咗, 你可以向律政師申請「訟費」拎返律師費, </em><br />\n但係法庭可以話因為你喺狗屋冇同班狗解釋/自銷嫌疑, 所以可以拒絕比返律師費你<br />\n呢個就係喺狗屋入面保持沉默嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>「唯一風險」</strong></span></span>。<br />\n就算法庭判你無辜, 你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拎唔返律師費</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係記住, 你<strong><em><ins>咁樣最多都係冇咗律師費</ins></em></strong>, 但係如果<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你講任何嘢都可能會成為證據指控自己</span></ins></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(呢到講到班狗可以點問你令你自己中伏, 有d長自己聽啦廢事打, (around 9:30~11:00))<br />\n<br />\n李大律師強調, 唔係叫大家講大話, 只係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><ins>你有箴默權利去保障自己</em>[/b]</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[u]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關於手提電話</span></ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>被捕嗰下千其唔好拎部電話出嚟</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n唔好諗住打比屋企人/律師, 因為一旦你解鎖咗班狗就可以檢取你部電話.<br />\n班狗係有權利喺當你被捕之後嘅任何時候檢取你嘅身上嘅所有物品, 特別喺示威現場<br />\n<br />\n因為多數喺示威現場都會被控告「非法集結」, 佢哋拎你電話就會去查下你係咪同其他人有預謀/串謀去呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以當你一拎電話出嚟解鎖/打電話, 佢就可以收你電話<br />\n千其唔好喺現場解鎖電話, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>可以去到警署先用警方電話打比屋企人幫你搵律師</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>電話係絕對唔需要比密碼佢</strong></span>, 佢要收, 比佢, 但係唔需要比密碼佢<br />\n除非佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>得到你嘅同意 </strong></span>or 佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有法庭搜查令</strong></span>, <br />\n否則你係唔需要同佢配合, 唔洗比密碼佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>閞於搜屋</ins></strong></span><br />\n佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇你同意</strong></span> or <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇搜查令</strong></span>, 係絕對唔可以去你屋企<br />\n班狗可能會同你講, 「如果你同意去你屋企搜, 快d搜完咪快d走」<br />\n但係可以自己諗, <em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你配合完佢係咪可以早d走, 如果唔係, 點解要配合佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em><br />\n如果真係去屋企搜查, 你<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可以要求有律師在場監查成個搜屋過程</strong></span><br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>Q&amp;A:</ins></strong></span><br />\n<em>1. 如果不幸喺拘留期間<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>遇到酷刑/屈打成招</strong></span></span>, 有咩可以做?</em><br />\n<br />\nA: 如果不幸被襲, 只能講希望有CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (不過當然好多時都無啦, 打得你一定會避)<br />\n咁你可以做嘅就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>記住嗰個地方/黑警個樣</strong></span></span>, <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為喺狗屋入面, 你去<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">每一個地方都會有記錄</span></strong>, <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>邊個黑警負責你都有記錄</strong></span>, <br />\n你只要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認到佢哋個樣</span></strong></span>, <br />\n就可以搵律師<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>要求搵值日官將嗰d黑警帶去你面前去認人</strong></span></span>, <br />\n然後律師就可以做相關工作幫你跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>Too long don't read</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. 「我無嘢講」係由你捕嗰刻開始直到律師嚟之前, <span style=\"color: red;\">對乜人 (包括手足/家長)都冇嘢講</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 「我無嘢講」唯一風險係打贏官司<span style=\"color: red;\">冇得拎返律師費</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 千其唔好解鎖手機/比密碼班狗, <span style=\"color: red;\">用狗屋電話搵家人/律師</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 狗隻除非有你同意/ 搜查令, 否則無權拎你手機密碼/ 上你屋企搜屋<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果被酷刑, 要<span style=\"color: red;\">認住黑警同嗰個地方個樣</span>, 然後請律師搵當值官認人+跟進"},{"pid":"cbf6221c7c38955d180e92971ce1b2cdc0db218d","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KanZhongGuo.web/videos/486314495263561/?v=486314495263561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKanZhongGuo.web%2Fvideos%2F486314495263561%2F%3Fv%3D486314495263561&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=ecc2870c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KanZhongGuo.web/videos/486314495263561/?v=486314495263561</a>"},{"pid":"a142b23431e7d26e3d89146f6a0f3e5ec23aea3a","tid":1516464,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f47103047b8e83914f687979c102cb0d7391a13","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:39:24.000Z","msg":"我係抄post既，因為我要全世界都知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住講多錯多，冇野講係對全世界包括父母 / 同行被拉手足 / 扮關心既警員都冇任何討論，唔傾計唔出聲 ( 除左你既律師同法官 )</span></span>"},{"pid":"c756ef8e85123b4c9e445f3861e984c4984d5e46","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"重要既post一兩日就沉點得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819c0d8351dd0d6439b19ccd72527a8ca78fa2ec","tid":1516464,"uid":231818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"343cf5e525ec284bd3bffc3bd861aa191ee9a6df","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:42:23.000Z","msg":"同黑警合作 = 比料佢地拉你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請保持沉默，比狗打要認樣，上警車前要對記者大聲講我而家冇骨折，全名(如果唔係律師揾唔到你)</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a68147f37c853189e5ee93148ca5bf39c831d96","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRPDu7T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRPDu7T.jpg&h=aa98c2d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86a980802a3ba0114422eaef7c3d4f6e6d334c05","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fecf071ab52240dde32f5c949af20e5f0b9b7d","tid":1516464,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822a9543fda306324a2e49681ad1aad217aa11cc","tid":1516464,"uid":148839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"